    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的电脑已被不明病毒严重感染，杀毒软件彻底失效。接着，你竟然变成了一个光标。现在，受命于危难之间，你将深入文件系统，找出这些制造混乱的病毒，拯救整个系统！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本次试玩版中，你将体验4种不同的光标，探索第一快硬盘，并可尝试一部分限定物品。你是会将整个系统清理干净，还是会揭开更可怕的真相？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/855100d251fc62af92367c256cb106e8.webp?t=1761225558\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.poster.avif?t=1761225558\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.webm?t=1761225558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.mp4?t=1761225558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《病毒识别：拯救系统》是一款以光标为核心的动作类肉鸽游戏，背景设定在你那被病毒感染的操作系统中。游戏将弹幕射击的紧张节奏感与文件系统的探索乐趣巧妙地融合在了一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入操作系统的世界，文件夹已然成为了危机四伏的地牢，文件中藏有秘密、宝藏，与之相伴的还有未知的危险。你将穿梭于程序生成的关卡之中，对抗无情的病毒，收集各种强大的EXE文件，让它们在你的冒险之旅中助你一臂之力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/df147b75a90d6132b227f571f8bdd2fe.webp?t=1761225558\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.poster.avif?t=1761225558\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.webm?t=1761225558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.mp4?t=1761225558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过多种可操控光标与成群病毒展开搏斗，每种光标都拥有独特的战斗风格。在每个被感染的硬盘最深处，都有一场残酷的Boss战等待着你。你准备好迎接挑战，扶大厦之将倾了吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263870/extras/089c426196bedd66e9c3a2ad4d7f3127.webp?t=1761225558\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仿佛穿梭于程序生成的地牢般探索文件系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以光标为核心的战斗机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种突发事件使你时刻保持警惕</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种难度与规则选项，打造个性化体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过30种独特病毒（还有闪光变种哦！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4场以上独特的Boss战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12种以上可供操控的光标！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超100种随机掉落物品等你来取</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超30种EXE文件，适配各种战斗风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光标外观</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >病毒图鉴会记录你发现的所有病毒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……还有隐藏的秘密？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多惊喜等你发掘</p></li></ul>",
